I’ve been using the platform a lot today, it and its been really impressive. I can tell there’s been a huge amount of progress over the last few weeks. :clap:

I did notice my units haven’t gone down much but i’ve been using the build app and the chat app a lot. Are we giving away too many free credits?

I've had the opposite experience lol.  Seems as though I can run outta credits extraordinarily quick in build mode.  If i want to test how my app works on 4 or 5 multi-page (<10) docs, I can  nearly instantly run out of credits
:ack: -- pricing model is going to change, so this discussion is probably moot :slightly_smiling_face:
